From: Stuart Henderson <stuarth@opensource.cirrus.com>
Date: Wed, 6 Mar 2024 16:14:35 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] ASoC: wm8962: Enable oscillator if selecting WM8962_FLL_OSC
Git-commit: 03c7874106ca5032a312626b927b1c35f07b1f35
Patch-mainline: v6.8
References: stable-fixes

Signed-off-by: Stuart Henderson <stuarth@opensource.cirrus.com>
Link: https://msgid.link/r/20240306161439.1385643-1-stuarth@opensource.cirrus.com
Signed-off-by: Mark Brown <broonie@kernel.org>
Acked-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

---
 sound/soc/codecs/wm8962.c | 4 ++++
 1 file changed, 4 insertions(+)

diff --git a/sound/soc/codecs/wm8962.c b/sound/soc/codecs/wm8962.c
index fb90ae6a8a34..6d7bb696b135 100644
--- a/sound/soc/codecs/wm8962.c
+++ b/sound/soc/codecs/wm8962.c
@@ -2914,8 +2914,12 @@ static int wm8962_set_fll(struct snd_soc_component *component, int fll_id, int s
 	switch (fll_id) {
 	case WM8962_FLL_MCLK:
 	case WM8962_FLL_BCLK:
+		fll1 |= (fll_id - 1) << WM8962_FLL_REFCLK_SRC_SHIFT;
+		break;
 	case WM8962_FLL_OSC:
 		fll1 |= (fll_id - 1) << WM8962_FLL_REFCLK_SRC_SHIFT;
+		snd_soc_component_update_bits(component, WM8962_PLL2,
+					      WM8962_OSC_ENA, WM8962_OSC_ENA);
 		break;
 	case WM8962_FLL_INT:
 		snd_soc_component_update_bits(component, WM8962_FLL_CONTROL_1,
